{"type":"message","id":"b6ae6785","parentId":"104fe7af","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:52:35.288Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_24b7a7f2caab41d28fa0a586","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"- 📦 [更多](#更多) — GUI · 飞书 · Notion · 诊断 · FAQ · 企业版 · 菠萝王朝\n\n---\n\n<a id=\"快速开始\"></a>\n\n## 🚀 快速开始\n\n> 🔴 **新手请用云服务器**，不要在个人电脑上安装。[→ 领一台免费服务器](./docs/server-setup.md)\n\n### 1️⃣ 选择制度\n\n安装时可选择三种制度：\n\n| 制度 | 特点 | 适用场景 | Agent |\n|------|------|---------|-------|\n| **明朝内阁制** | 司礼监 + 内阁 + 六部，快速迭代 | 个人项目 | 18 个 |\n| **唐朝三省制** | 中书→门下→尚书，制衡审核 | 偏好严谨流程的项目 | 14 个 |\n| **现代企业制** | CEO/CTO/CFO，国际化 | 创业团队 | 14 个 |\n\n### 2️⃣ 一键安装\n--\n<summary><h2>🖥️ GUI 管理界面</h2></summary>\n\n内置 Web Dashboard（`gui/` 目录），React + TypeScript + Vite：\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"./images/gui-court.png\" alt=\"朝堂总览\" width=\"90%\" />\n  <br/><em>朝堂总览 — 御座、六部、诸院，在线状态一目了然</em>\n</p>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":17,"aggregated":"- 📦 [更多](#更多) — GUI · 飞书 · Notion · 诊断 · FAQ · 企业版 · 菠萝王朝\n\n---\n\n<a id=\"快速开始\"></a>\n\n## 🚀 快速开始\n\n> 🔴 **新手请用云服务器**，不要在个人电脑上安装。[→ 领一台免费服务器](./docs/server-setup.md)\n\n### 1️⃣ 选择制度\n\n安装时可选择三种制度：\n\n| 制度 | 特点 | 适用场景 | Agent |\n|------|------|---------|-------|\n| **明朝内阁制** | 司礼监 + 内阁 + 六部，快速迭代 | 个人项目 | 18 个 |\n| **唐朝三省制** | 中书→门下→尚书，制衡审核 | 偏好严谨流程的项目 | 14 个 |\n| **现代企业制** | CEO/CTO/CFO，国际化 | 创业团队 | 14 个 |\n\n### 2️⃣ 一键安装\n--\n<summary><h2>🖥️ GUI 管理界面</h2></summary>\n\n内置 Web Dashboard（`gui/` 目录），React + TypeScript + Vite：\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"./images/gui-court.png\" alt=\"朝堂总览\" width=\"90%\" />\n  <br/><em>朝堂总览 — 御座、六部、诸院，在线状态一目了然</em>\n</p>","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774151555283}}
{"type":"message","id":"1a10042a","parentId":"b6ae6785","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:52:38.441Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要安装Dashboard。让我检查一下gui目录的README，看看如何启动Dashboard服务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_650a501d27e04017a0d6c72a","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/projects/danghuangshang/gui/README.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_af916428d36b4441bfca64c6","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/projects/danghuangshang/gui/package.json"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":900,"output":70,"cacheRead":61568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62538,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774151555289}}
{"type":"message","id":"db5e13b7","parentId":"1a10042a","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:52:38.539Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_650a501d27e04017a0d6c72a","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 🖥️ 菠萝王朝 GUI — Web 管理后台\n\n> ← [返回项目 README](../README.md) | [📖 GUI 文档](../docs/gui.md)\n\n基于 React + TypeScript + Vite 构建的 AI 朝廷 Web 管理后台。\n\n## 功能\n\n- **仪表盘** — 各部门状态、Token 消耗、系统负载\n- **朝堂** — Web 端与各部门 Bot 对话\n- **会话管理** — 历史会话、消息详情、Token 统计\n- **定时任务** — 可视化管理 Cron（启用/禁用/手动触发）\n- **系统健康** — CPU/内存/磁盘监控\n\n## 快速启动\n\n```bash\n# 1. 构建前端\ncd gui && npm install && npm run build\n\n# 2. 启动后端（设置登录密码）\ncd server && npm install\nBOLUO_AUTH_TOKEN=你的密码 node index.js\n```\n\n访问 `http://你的服务器IP:18795`\n\n> 📖 详细说明见 [GUI 文档](../docs/gui.md)\n\n## 技术栈\n\n- React 18 + TypeScript\n- Vite 构建\n- Express.js 后端代理\n- OpenClaw Gateway API\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774151558523}}
{"type":"message","id":"a9734747","parentId":"db5e13b7","timestamp":"2026-03-22T03:52:38.550Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_af916428d36b4441bfca64c6","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"name\": \"boluo-gui-frontend\",\n  \"private\": true,\n  \"version\": \"0.0.0\",\n  \"type\": \"module\",\n  \"scripts\": {\n    \"dev\": \"vite\",\n    \"build\": \"tsc -b && vite build\",\n    \"lint\": \"eslint .\",\n    \"preview\": \"vite preview\"\n  },\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@tailwindcss/vite\": \"^4.2.1\",\n    \"react\": \"^19.2.0\",\n    \"react-dom\": \"^19.2.0\",\n    \"recharts\": \"^3.7.0\",\n    \"tailwindcss\": \"^4.2.1\"\n  },\n  \"devDependencies\": {\n    \"@eslint/js\": \"^9.39.1\",\n    \"@types/node\": \"^24.10.1\",\n    \"@types/react\": \"^19.2.7\",\n    \"@types/react-dom\": \"^19.2.3\",\n    \"@vitejs/plugin-react\": \"^5.1.1\",\n    \"eslint\": \"^9.39.1\",\n    \"eslint-plugin-react-hooks\": \"^7.0.1\",\n    \"eslint-plugin-react-refresh\": \"^0.4.24\",\n    \"globals\": \"^16.5.0\",\n    \"typescript\": \"~5.9.3\",\n    \"typescript-eslint\": \"^8.48.0\",\n    \"vite\": \"^7.3.1\"\n  }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774151558540}}
